> **Prompt:** 31yo woman, baby face, sweet smile, dimples, **(perfect W-sitting pose on floor:1.5)**, knees touching, feet spread out to sides, **(white cotton tights:1.4)**, **(bulky diaper visible under tights:1.4)**, short smock top, exposed belly button, hands clapping, indoor lighting, 8k.

